                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18301028-159-off881 t18301028-159-crimeloc884"></join>. On the 8th of October, about two minutes after I had used these scales, I heard they were stolen off the counter - I heard them drop; I ordered a witness to run-I followed, and met the prisoner in Old-street, in the custody of the officer, who had them in his hand-this was five minutes after I had heard them fall.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18301028-159-person1361">
                  JAMES 
                  CROSS
               <interp inst="t18301028-159-person1361" type="surname" value="CROSS"></interp>
